title: The Return of Sherlock Holmes - BBC Radio Drama - Set 4 - Seymou
description:
The Return of Sherlock Holmes by Sir Arthur Conan Doyle. (published 1903)

Dramatised for radio by Bert Coules et al. Starring Clive Merrison as Sherlock Holmes & Michael Williams as Doctor John Watson.

Thirteen stories, each lasting 45 minutes. Total running time approximately 9? hours.

The Empty House.

The Norwood Builder.

The Dancing Men.

The Solitary Cyclist.

The Priory School.

Black Peter.

Charles Augustus Milverton.

The Six Napoleons.

The Three Students.

The Golden Pince-nez.

The Missing Three-quarter.

The Abbey Grange.

The Second Stain.

My recordings from BBC7 at 160kbps CBR joint-stereo mp3, encoded with LAME.
Recorded from Freeview -> DVD Recorder -> MP3.

Have fun & please seed.

SeymourDAC :)
